These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, lemonade, mirinda, cola, hot-chocolate, almond-milk
There are 7 different nationalities: nigerian, indian, argentine, canadian, spanish, indonesian, thai
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, rowing, climbing, skiing, rugby, weightlifting, biathlon
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, tram, car, scooter, snowmobile
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is rugby is the canadian##1
 3. the person driving the car is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 4. the indian is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the nigerian is on the right of the thai##1
 6. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the spanish##1
 8. the person driving the tram is between the person driving the snowmobile and the indonesian##2
 9. the spanish is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person drinking cola##1
12. the person drinking cola is the person driving the helicopter##1
13. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the argentine##1
14. the indonesian is the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the thai##1
16. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
17. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the argentine##1
18. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the spanish##1
19. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Beverage      | milk  | hot-chocolate        | cola | lemonade      | mirinda     | iced-tea      | almond-milk     |
| Nationality   | indian | canadian         | thai   | nigerian | indonesian    | spanish | argentine |
